Motorists have been adviced to use alternative routes, as the N4 west between R80 and Ga-Rankuwa in Pretoria has been closed off after a cash-in-transit heist. Pretoria – N4 West: #CrimeScene Cash Heist before the Ga-Rankuwa exit – SLOW TRAFFIC pic.twitter.com/0ZpZyMfU2o — Rob Beezy (@TrafficSA) February 23, 2018 It is reported that armed robbers managed to flee the scene with an undisclosed amount of money. No injuries have been reported. More to follow as the story develops… 